title: FRIDAY 3/19 - Mitchell Trubisky shuffles off to Buffalo

description:
The Bills securing a backup for Josh Allen as Mitchell Trubisky head to Buffalo(0:09) while new Bears QB Andy Dalton (0:23) talks about his decision to sign with Chicago. Will Fuller (1:11) takes his talents to South Beach and Kyle Rudolph (3:01) heads to the Big Apple, while the Raiders add some backfield depth (4:07)
